summary: Wanted
title: Wanted
body:
read it on the AO3 at http://bit.ly/2X96eQ3

by hardlyfatal

Brienne needs a handsome, exciting pretend husband to fend off her friend’s plan to shove her into an arranged marriage. She’s got a list of prospects, she’s checked it twice, and she’s off to Dorne to interview the first one: Jaime Lannister. If he won’t do it, well, she’s certain Oberyn Martell will, or Ramsay Snow, or perhaps even The Mountain?

Jaime’s getting tired of hunting bounties, but that’s a day in the park compared to the trouble this enormous madwoman is causing him. His conscience picked a fine time to make a reappearance, or at least that’s the reason he’s telling himself for why he can’t leave her alone.

Or: the author can’t stop plugging these two into weird scenarios. Send help.
